{"tid":1540312,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"跳閘出太高風險？我有計！","createTime":"2019-09-04T11:15:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T00:59:31.000Z","uid":53377,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7b0d07570bbb48defb578a35353f26d68cc93183","tid":1540312,"uid":53377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:15:10.000Z","msg":"相信有唔少手足怕跳閘時被粉紅人或站內黑社會截停 有見及此 推薦一個安全方法俾大家：<br />\n<br />\n1. 每次起點入閘都嘟卡 <br />\n2. 到終點後去客服同職員講 買車飛唔見撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3. 佢會俾張出閘卡你出閘 如下<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7vX6Wem.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7vX6Wem.png&h=0053b0f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n4. 下次入閘前去客服話入唔到閘 佢會幫你搞番上次無出閘問題 不扣錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"496c0733a40e701f1c99fc03faec2448745843a5","tid":1540312,"uid":53377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:16:30.000Z","msg":"一連"},{"pid":"2971f06f282f1caad7181a7180832184258bb2f6","tid":1540312,"uid":53377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:17:24.000Z","msg":"二連"},{"pid":"c3e2bd4a4003aeda9f51b294fba6ea0e1392c5b3","tid":1540312,"uid":53377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:17:46.000Z","msg":"三連"},{"pid":"4981566ff93a85258012df61fbf9d4d23ac540ff","tid":1540312,"uid":53377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:18:48.000Z","msg":"四連"},{"pid":"4705ef9b01d75c8e973d9511b12b7778ea472251","tid":1540312,"uid":53377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:19:17.000Z","msg":"五連"},{"pid":"5808cce7bb850f397072f9520acca6ecb693fc24","tid":1540312,"uid":53377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:19:29.000Z","msg":"六連"},{"pid":"6b1c302962e0